{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbf82bc54-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12624"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12624"},"text":"§ 12624.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Evaluations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Pursuant to the provisions for evaluations conducted under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12639"},"text":"section 12639 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and in particular subsection (g) of such section, the Corporation shall conduct periodic evaluations of the National Civilian Community Corps Program authorized under this division. Upon completing each such evaluation, the Corporation shall transmit to the authorizing committees a report on the evaluation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbf82bc55-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/610/tI/s164"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–610, title I, § 164","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 195M, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/484/dA/tX/s1092/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–484, div. A, title X, § 1092(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-23"},"text":"Oct. 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/2532"},"text":"106 Stat. 2532","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 164 and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/82/tI/s104/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–82, title I, § 104(b)","children":[],"tail":", title IV, § 402(b)(2), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-09-21"},"text":"Sept. 21, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/840"},"text":"107 Stat. 840","children":[],"tail":", 919; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/13/tI/s1514"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–13, title I, § 1514","children":[],"tail":",